.Dt ADB 4 macppc
.Os 

.Sh NAME
.Nm adb
.Nd Apple Desktop Bus driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "adb at macobio?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The Apple Desktop Bus driver handles I/O devices such as ADB Keyboard, pointing
devices such as trackball or mouse, and special function buttons.
